#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:17
msgid "Model Weight"
msgstr "模型权重"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:19
msgid ""
"`GLM-5.2`(BF16 version)require 2 Atlas 800 A3 (128G × 8) node or 4 Atlas "
"800 A2 (64G × 8) node.: [Download model "
"weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.2)."
msgstr ""
"`GLM-5.2`(BF16版本)需要2个Atlas 800 A3 (128G × 8)节点或4个Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)节点：[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.2)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:20
msgid ""
"`GLM-5.2-w8a8`: require 1 Atlas 800 A3 (128G × 8) node or 2 Atlas 800 A2 "
"(64G × 8) node.[Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models"
"/Eco-Tech/GLM-5.2-w8a8)."
msgstr ""
"`GLM-5.2-w8a8`：需要1个Atlas 800 A3 (128G × 8)节点或2个Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/GLM-5.2-w8a8)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:21
msgid ""
"You can use [msmodelslim](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/msmodelslim) to "
"quantify the model naively."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用[msmodelslim](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/msmodelslim)对模型进行朴素量化。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:23
msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of"
" multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`"
msgstr ""
"建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录中，例如`/root/.cache/`"

