#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:403
msgid "Co-located Deployment on 4 Nodes (200k context)"
msgstr "4节点共置部署(200k上下文)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:405
msgid ""
"In a co-located (mixed) deployment, prefill and decode run together on "
"the same nodes, in contrast to the disaggregated setup below. The "
"following templates deploy `GLM-5.2` across 4 nodes with `DP4 TP8` "
"(`data-parallel-size-local=1` per node), a 200k context window, and MTP "
"(`num_speculative_tokens=5`). Node 0 hosts the API server and is the DP "
"master; Node 1 to Node 3 run with `--headless`. Prefix caching is "
"disabled (`--no-enable-prefix-caching`) in this configuration. All IPs, "
"NIC names, ports and weight paths are placeholders."
msgstr ""
"在共置(混合)部署中，prefill和decode在同一节点上运行，与下文分离式部署不同。以下模板在4个节点上部署`GLM-5.2`，采用`DP4 TP8`(每节点`data-parallel-size-local=1`)、200k上下文窗口和MTP(`num_speculative_tokens=5`)。节点0托管API服务器并作为DP主节点；节点1至节点3以`--headless`运行。此配置中禁用前缀缓存(`--no-enable-prefix-caching`)。所有IP、网卡名称、端口和权重路径均为占位符。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:407
msgid "**Node 0** (API server / DP master):"
msgstr "**节点0**(API服务器/DP主节点)："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:464
msgid "**Node 1** (headless, `--data-parallel-start-rank 1`):"
msgstr "**节点1**(无头模式，`--data-parallel-start-rank 1`)："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.md:523
msgid ""
"Node 2 and Node 3 use the same script as Node 1, with `--data-parallel-"
"start-rank` set to `2` and `3` respectively (and `node0_ip` pointing to "
"Node 0)."
msgstr ""
"节点2和节点3使用与节点1相同的脚本，`--data-parallel-start-rank`分别设置为`2`和`3`(且`node0_ip`指向节点0)。"

